                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-603443265" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="603443265">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiaonasen/">乔纳森</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">论述清晰有力。专谈海德格尔的一章，即可视为《存在与时间》简明而出色的导读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="395142406">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-395142406" class="vote-count">1</span>
